# Execution Profile PowerShell Export

- exportId: `<%= it.exportId %>`
- SuiteType: `<%= it.suiteType %>`
- ExecutionProfile: `<%= it.executionProfile %>`
- ExecutionPolicy: `<%= it.executionPolicy %>`
- SourceRunStatus: `<%= it.sourceRunStatus %>`
- ReplayPackageType: `<%= it.replayPackageType %>`
- IncludeResolvedSecrets: `<%= it.includeResolvedSecrets ? "true" : "false" %>`
- IncludeRuntimeStartup: `<%= it.includeRuntimeStartup ? "true" : "false" %>`
- IncludeHealthcheckGate: `<%= it.includeHealthcheckGate ? "true" : "false" %>`

## Plan Order

<%= it.planOrderMarkdown %>

<% if (Array.isArray(it.jmeterArtifactPathsRel) && it.jmeterArtifactPathsRel.length > 0) { %>
## JMeter Artifacts

